- Constants: 0 (initial Set/Map), 3, 2 = let me count: 0 (nullish coalescing default), 1 (increment), 3 (comparison), 2 (comparison) = 4 constants = 4
- Assignments: liveSet = ..., neighborCounts = new Map, neighborCounts.set(...), nextLiveCells = [] = 4 assignments = 24
