I'll refactor `neighborKeys` to use a pre-computed offsets constant instead of nested loops. This will:
1. Better reveal intent - the 8 neighbor offsets are explicit data, not computed
2. Reduce mass significantly - eliminating 2 loops, multiple assignments, and a conditional
3. Be more declarative

